Usage: FORMAT PUBLIC_ACTION <format description>
  Controls how public CTCP ACTIONs appear.

  Valid format characters:
       F          Nick of person doing action
       T          Channel receiving action
       M          The action message

See Also:  
  ME
  DESCRIBE
